Interface EddystoneListener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    SimpleEddystoneListener

    public interface EddystoneListener
    Listener used to report Eddystone scanning results.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods

      void onEddystoneDiscovered(IEddystoneDevice eddystone, IEddystoneNamespace namespace)
      Called when Eddystone is discovered for the first time.
      void onEddystoneLost(IEddystoneDevice eddystone, IEddystoneNamespace namespace)

    • Method Detail

      • onEddystoneDiscovered

        void onEddystoneDiscovered(IEddystoneDevice eddystone,
                           IEddystoneNamespace namespace)
        Called when Eddystone is discovered for the first time. This will be called only once per scan or after beacon is reported lost.
        Parameters:
        eddystone - IEddystoneDevice instance.
        namespace - IEddystoneNamespace instance.

      • onEddystonesUpdated

        void onEddystonesUpdated(java.util.List<IEddystoneDevice> eddystones,
                         IEddystoneNamespace namespace)
        Called when Eddystones are updated.
        Parameters:
        eddystones - List of updated IEddystoneDevice devices.
        namespace - IEddystoneNamespace instance.

      • onEddystoneLost

        void onEddystoneLost(IEddystoneDevice eddystone,
                     IEddystoneNamespace namespace)
        Called when Eddystone is reported lost (out of range). onEddystoneDiscovered will be called when beacon is back in range.
        Parameters:
        eddystone - Lost IBeaconDevice instance.
        namespace - IBeaconRegion instance.
